00:12:18.334 --> 00:12:22.244
So you know that an intervention works in a specific space and now you want to

204
00:12:22.284 --> 00:12:26.074
adapt and tailor it to your space and make it work to serve your

205
00:12:26.104 --> 00:12:28.364
community. So we have frameworks for that as well.

206
00:12:29.204 --> 00:12:33.184
The next bucket of methods are

207
00:12:33.244 --> 00:12:37.224
to help us develop strategies, specifically to accelerate and improve

208
00:12:37.264 --> 00:12:40.724
the adoption, implementation, and sustainment of different

209
00:12:40.804 --> 00:12:44.784
EBIs. And these last two are actually less leveraged, which I think is a

