00:12:52.584 --> 00:12:56.244
How do we deimplement those and really provide the

213
00:12:56.284 --> 00:12:59.384
highest quality care possible for the populations we serve?

214
00:12:59.824 --> 00:13:01.924
And then how do we disseminate and scale up?

215
00:13:01.984 --> 00:13:05.724
How do we take something that we know works within a specific HIV

216
00:13:05.824 --> 00:13:09.744
clinic, for example, and scale it up nationally so that the entire network

217
00:13:09.784 --> 00:13:12.874
of people with HIV can receive that high-quality care?

218
00:13:14.784 --> 00:13:18.764
So this is kind of summarizing quickly for us the different stages

219
00:13:18.804 --> 00:13:21.144
or the life course of program implementation.

220
00:13:21.204 --> 00:13:24.404
We start off, this is a graph here of the

