00:13:24.944 --> 00:13:28.184
life course, if you will, of real-world evidence over time.

222
00:13:28.584 --> 00:13:32.064
We start off thinking about could a program work? Does it work?

223
00:13:32.604 --> 00:13:34.504
Is it effective? Is it efficacious?

