00:14:23.744 --> 00:14:27.024
practice. You ask yourselves or the group a couple of questions.

238
00:14:27.104 --> 00:14:29.584
Is it efficacious? Is it effective?

239
00:14:30.004 --> 00:14:33.613
And if the answer to that is yes on both fronts, then you are at the stage of

240
00:14:33.624 --> 00:14:36.924
developing a hybrid effectiveness trial or conducting

241
00:14:38.064 --> 00:14:40.944
implementation research like we're doing in my R1.

242
00:14:43.004 --> 00:14:46.384
This is a very simplified, but the

