00:43:43.196 --> 00:43:46.716
be a lower lift from a resource perspective for

736
00:43:46.776 --> 00:43:50.486
the sites to keep their patient population up to

737
00:43:50.556 --> 00:43:50.796
date.

738
00:43:54.576 --> 00:43:58.476
So, I'm going to tell you a little bit about two of the practices,

739
00:43:59.296 --> 00:44:03.236
clinic A and clinic B. They are both in the same FQHC system, which is

740
00:44:03.276 --> 00:44:06.976
a disadvantage. This was a feasibility pilot also, so what we

741
00:44:07.016 --> 00:44:10.636
learned was that what they report to the UDS measures are actually

